HI its early and im just waiting for some of my usual morning friends to get on and say hi.. Ive been cleaning tonight... But Yes I went out and hung with Rhi Rhi it was alot of fun. I bought a new hoodie witch i must say is Plaid as in fuckin sweet. And then We went to Dinner and somehow someone fucked up my Gift Card and and over charged my shit a week ago there was really nothing that could be done but the manager was really cool and gave me gave me a little compensation which he really had no obligation to do.. yet my boy will be going to talk to the Htown one maybe and seeign what sup cus we think the waiter last time gipped us and got a nice 17 dolor Tip... Who Knoes.. anyways I still could care less Im feeling good... Peas for the night...
Tracy

Ok so ive been back in austin since sunday and yeah ITs going good.. My 2 classes rule. I love them so much.. I just completed my first week and tonight I met Sarah... I had a lot of fun and my Hot chocolate was very good. I hope she had fun.. we didn't have all the time in the world but maybe she will want to hang out again.:) I'm just worried because of what happened with the last girl I met... Not reasons on her behalf.. just maybe something is wrong with me and I don't see it.. well till later...
Tracy

Yeah weird night.. I'm really not gonna go to much into details... I Meet a girl.. She convinces me to believe. Makes me happy. Gains My trust. We Meet up. Hour goes by... I must go... get a call... Its a mistake... I go home, hurt and confused... While on the phone with the mistake... Feelings on phone but not in person still....One hour judgement.... I'm confused ....More to continue.... why....

Although Britt Called and she really made me Happy... Were building a super tree house... Its gonna be Plad....:) snow.....
Feeling better..... almost midnight wanna post before then. not much to say.... tomorrow looks to be a better day..

Good News, I am going to get to watch the 311 pay per view. 20 bux but well worth it. I'm happy bout that yet all sorts of confused. Hoping it will pass like most everything does with time, anyways. be back later tonight like always..
Tracy...

Im back and also bored no one is around and i feel tired. SomeOne get online and talk to me..... serene was good. anyways till later...
 Tracy

I'm up,  and this is early for once... I'm going to see serene play in a little while there music puts me in a good mood. as for now I'm just trying to open my eyes. Talk to this later.... I must go... 
  Tracy:)

Gosh This Year has started out so nice... Certain things and people have just made it nice. Ive goten back in to my woodworking stuff a little which is sweet. I also have played my guitar so much more. I miss Austin In my own Little ways but im still enjoying Being Home... My apt is so prefabricated it just wont ever seem to be my own little dwelling.. But its nice. I seem to have My own dressing room of sorts unless they move somone into that extra room with out my knowledge and if thats the case i may get kicked out... but who needs them.... lol.... As we speak I miss my CKY dvds and my tummy is happy. I also am working on another guitar thta ive had for a few years but never had an idea for till now. I know im neglecting my site but i have what you call designers block. I want everyone who reads this to check out this band. (which is maybe one person. www.musictx.com/serene very good frinds with a killer sound... I wish them the best. anyways today was good.... I had pizza with my mom. and I slept way to late as usual. Im off for now... Speaking with danny of serene they play at 3 yay... bye bye....

This is My first Entry Thought I would start it for the new year to kinda help me gather my thoughts on everyday. Also will be incorporating it in to Trunk Tribe as well as the other members of the Tribe. Many More things to come. Just wait and see... I'm happy............
